      "stem": "An 8 year old girl is examined by her GP and is noted to be short for her age and pale. An X-ray is performed to assess bone age, which reveals the predicted bone age to be 6 years, and shows dense bands within the metaphyses of the metacarpals. What is the most likely diagnosis?",
