      "stem": "A neonate is found to have a left kidney measuring 5.4 cm, right kidney 4.3 cm. A subsequent IVU demonstrates a complete duplication of the left kidney. The patient returns for follow-up IVU late in childhood. Which of the following signs would be unexpected?",
