      "stem": "An 18 month old, ambulatory girl presents with irritability and genu varum. On examination there is delayed dentition. Knee x-rays show bilateral widening with irregularity of the metaphyses, widening of the epiphyseal plates and coarse medullary trabeculation. What is the most likely diagnosis?",
