      "stem": "A 4 week old ex-premature baby has a witnessed seizure. A cranial US is performed which shows cystic structures bilaterally, adjacent to the trigone of the lateral ventricles. Which of the following favours a diagnosis of chronic periventricular leukomalacia over porencephaly?",
